::KitKat::

Hears the vioce on her commlink. "I'm here on my own.  I got the 
scent of a strange wolf out here and I'm following my nose.  Where 
are you?" she saw a huge shadow on the ground. She looked up and saw 
Terrorsaur. "OH,, Never mind.  But what are you  doing out here?"


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Talon Harvilicz" <wilddance_mare@h...> 
wrote:
> Terrorsaur:
> 
> 
> Terrorsaur kept a good altitude. He was actually enjoying this long 
range 
> trip. He was cold, but that was all. He still had his air 
superiority. He 
> was almost past the last marker that strange little Fuzor gave him. 
And 
> after that, he would find Rowdy Wolf.
> 
> Knowing he said he would fire on him didn't make him feel safe, but 
he was 
> quite a marksman himself. He was fast and skilled.
> 
> He had a feeling that he was being followed. He turned his head, 
seeing only 
> a small dot on the ground. He used his scanners to find out who it 
was, and 
> found out that it was only KitKat, one of the Predacons.
> 
> He opened his comm-link to her. "What are you doing out here? Did 
somebody 
> send you?"
